---
title: Quick Sweet Chilli Prawn & Veggie Stir-Fry with Udon Noodles
description: Prawns that are popping with delicious taste sensations, we say yes please! You won’t be able to get enough of these bad boys in a saucy sweet chilli stir-fry. Set off the flavour fireworks with ginger and oyster sauce stirred through, and udon noodles to slurp it all up.

*This recipe is under 550kcal per serving.*
